## üõ†Ô∏è Setup Instructions

### Install Dart and Flutter SDK
- **macOS or Linux:**
  - Download the Flutter SDK from the [official website](https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/install).
  - Extract the compressed files.
  - Add the Flutter tool to your system PATH.

- **Windows:**
  - Download the Flutter SDK from the [official website](https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/install).
  - Run the installer.
  - Add the Flutter tool to your system PATH.

### Configure Your IDE or Code Editor
- **Android Studio or IntelliJ IDEA:**
  - Install the Flutter and Dart plugins from the marketplace.
  
- **Visual Studio Code:**
  - Install the Flutter and Dart extensions from the marketplace.
  
- **Other IDEs or Code Editors:**
  - Check the [official Flutter documentation](https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/editor) for setup instructions.

### Verify Installation
Run the following command to check your Flutter installation status and identify any missing dependencies:
```bash
flutter doctor
